{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"41ff2ed7c5","title":"中共中央关于一九五O年东北工业投资及上缴款问题给东北局的批复","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ae02dd5e64","index":0,"year":1949,"month":11,"day":20,"articleId":"41ff2ed7c5"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0c1fb35ada","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于一九五O年东北工业投资及上缴款问题给东北局的批复","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"41ff2ed7c5"},{"id":"9510deea1b","type":"appellation","text":"东北局：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"41ff2ed7c5"},{"id":"d578e0ad09","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）空、海军及高射炮款均在第一、第二两个年度之一亿二千万美元中扣除。但因该项价格不明，难说应扣款数。你们的计算，应以一九五O年支用四千万美元作东北工业投资为妥。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"41ff2ed7c5"},{"id":"7543e3dd87","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）你们上缴中央之款，希望你们考虑可否多缴些，尤其是粮食一项。因京津附近今年水灾，目前民粮已由京津向乡下倒流，估计明年更甚。如京津粮食供应不上，则对全国影响很坏。如何请研究后复。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"41ff2ed7c5"},{"id":"ac036f897a","type":"paragraph","text":" 中  央","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"41ff2ed7c5"}],"page":{"id":"56b7a58bbf","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"41ff2ed7c5","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}